parameters:
Memimi: Ah...! Not again, my photo is up at the school
gate...!

Memimi: Grrr... No matter how many times I peel them off,
someone keeps putting them back up... Why would someone
expose my embarrassing photos for all the passersby to
see...? And everyone at school looks at them so much...

Male Student: President Memimi, you were originally from an
orphanage, right? It seems to be gone now, but to earn your
own tuition, enroll in the academy, and even become the
student council president must have taken extraordinary
effort.

Memimi: Back at the orphanage, I was the oldest and always
took care of the other kids... Ironically, if it hadn't been
shut down and I hadn't been picked up by the big boss, I
probably wouldn't have even pursued further education. I was
always good at studying, but I really worked hard in the
months leading up to the entrance exams...

Male Student: You're so caring and hardworking, truly
amazing... It's precisely because of that personality that
even when you're told to do a masturbation live stream, you
don't run away and you see it through... hehe...

Memimi: ...If it's just me suffering and everything works
out smoothly, then I'll do whatever it takes... There are...
limits though... ugh... uhh...

Male Student: Could the next Monster Fight be Shark Duke's
last match...? Even if the city's organizations merge, or if
he becomes an AV actress, the way we conduct our monster
activities will change completely, right?

Memimi: Eh, I really don't think he'll become an AV actress
no matter what... Even if we win and the strongest
organization is formed, there will still be many small,
defiant groups. I don't think Monster Fights will
disappear...

Male Student: (Aside from Monster Fights, even if he becomes
an AV actress, I wonder if he'll continue as the student
council president... It's super exciting to think that a
girl from the same school could star in AV... I hope she
keeps attending school...)

Memimi: (This guy is thinking about such indecent things...
Appearing in AV is seriously no joke... I absolutely can't
lose, for my own protection...)

Male Student: Rumor has it that Dynamite Abalone is a former
sumo wrestler, and he even made it quite far in his
career... With over 150 kilos difference in weight, it's
going to be a tough fight for Duke Shark...

Memimi: Ah, but that's just a rumor... Fighting isn't about
weight... It's about guts, guts...

Male Student: I heard from my brother that ever since Orca
Mayor took office five years ago, he's been funneling money
only to businesses and facilities that benefit him. He's
been pocketing a lot of the tax money and taking kickbacks
from his subsidiary companies...

Memimi: Many of the monsters are the wretched result of
those who refused to follow him or were abandoned... Even
now, as you enjoy your school life, you never know when you
might be robbed of it... Just don't let your guard down
around him...

Male Student: (But if Orca Mayor wins, the president will
make her AV debut... I just can't help wanting to support
the mayor... I really want to see the president's AV...)
Memimi: Hey, don't trust him... Are you listening? Huh...!

Memimi: Ah...! Not again, my photo is up at the school
gate...!

Memimi: Grrr... Lately, no matter how many times I peel them
off, someone keeps putting them back up... Why would someone
display my embarrassing photos for all the passersby to
see...? And everyone at school sees them too...

Male Student: After graduating from the academy, will
President Memimi dedicate herself to the activities of the
dark organization? With a convenience store around, you
won't have to worry about finding a job, right?

Memimi: Hmm... I plan to go to university, but after that, I
can't really imagine what I'll do... For now... I don't
think I'll leave Dorietoku City...

Memimi: Anyway, for now, I need to deal with various things
in front of me... There's too much to think about other than
myself...

Male Student: Well, since you did erotic broadcasts under
your real name, it would be difficult to find a job outside
the city where people don't know the situation. If you were
an AV actress, I think you'd have plenty of offers...

Memimi: Shut up... In a few months, all that will be
forgotten by society... It has to be... Absolutely...
*muttering*

Male Student: I had heard rumors, but I never knew the mayor
of Dorietoku City was such a bad guy... He even gave
speeches at events, but I never listened seriously, so I
didn't recognize his face...

Memimi: I'm embarrassed to admit it, but... I wonder how
many people can actually remember the face of the mayor of
the municipality they live in? It can't be helped...

Memimi: Ah...! Not again, my photo is up at the school
gate...!

Memimi: Grrr... Lately, no matter how many times I peel them
off, someone keeps putting them back up... Why would someone
display my embarrassing photos for all the passersby to
see...? And everyone at school is looking at them so much...

Memimi: Ah...! Not again, my photo is up at the school
gate...!

Memimi: Grrr... Lately, no matter how many times I peel them
off, someone keeps putting them back up... Why would they
expose someone's embarrassing photos for all the passersby
to see...? And everyone at school is looking at them so
much...

Memimi: Ah...! Not again, my photo is up at the school
gate...!

Memimi: Grrr... No matter how many times I peel them off,
someone keeps putting them back up... Why would someone
display my embarrassing photos for all the passersby to
see...? And everyone at school sees them too...

Female Student: Lately, there's been a bit of a craze among
the girls in town over the monsters. They're comical but
strong, and their manliness is irresistible... My favorite
is Shark Broccoli-sama, the great leader!

Memimi: The monsters, once known for not being popular, are
finally seeing the light of day... If the great leader knew
how popular they are among the girls, he'd be delighted.
Although, there are quite a few scumbags among the
monsters...

Female Student: Of course, there are also plenty of girls
who are fans of Orca Asparagus-sama!! Despite facing
terrible fates, they never give up and continue to fight,
which makes them seem more manly than the average male
monster...

Memimi: Is that so... I wonder if I should be happy about
that...

Female Student: If we defeat the mayor, Shark Broccoli—the
great boss—will become the new mayor, right? And Vice Boss
Memimi, you'll become the second most important person in
the city! Your future is secure, isn't it?

Memimi: I wonder about that... I don't feel like I'll be
involved in city politics... Besides, fixing all the various
things that are falling apart in the city will be quite a
heavy responsibility, far from secure...
